    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
            Память нагрузка CPU сервера приложений
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0">
                <iframe src="https://play.grafana.org/d-solo/000000003/graphite3a-sample-website-dashboard?orgId=1&from=1747715287498&to=1747718901498&timezone=browser&panelId=4&__feature.dashboardSceneSolo" width="100%" height="300" frameborder="0"></iframe>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
                Количество запросов к микросервисам
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0">
                <iframe src="https://play.grafana.org/d-solo/000000003/graphite3a-sample-website-dashboard?orgId=1&from=1747715287498&to=1747718901498&timezone=browser&panelId=2&__feature.dashboardSceneSolo" width="100%" height="300" frameborder="0"></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

